## <a id="user"></a>User Management ##
Use these commands to create and delete users from the BOSH Director.

<table border="1" class="nice" >
  <tr>
    <th>Command</th>
    <th>Description</th>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><code>create user [USERNAME] [PASSWORD]</code></td>
	<td>Creates a user with the BOSH Director. Prompts you for a <code>USERNAME</code> and <code>PASSWORD</code> if you omit this information.</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
